---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const seo = {
  title: 'Vitamin Injections | D-Essence Wellness',
  description:
    'Targeted B12, B complex, vitamin C, and custom nutrient shots to support energy, immune health, and overall wellness—administered by trained professionals.',
  canonical: '/services/vitamin-injections/',
  type: 'website',
  jsonLd: [
    {
      '@context': 'https://schema.org',
      '@type': 'Service',
      name: 'Vitamin Injections',
      serviceType: 'Wellness & IV',
      areaServed: 'New Windsor, New York',
      url: 'https://dessencewellness.com/services/vitamin-injections/',
      provider: {
        '@type': 'MedicalBusiness',
        name: 'D-Essence Wellness',
        address: {
          '@type': 'PostalAddress',
          streetAddress: '871 Blooming Grove Turnpike Suite 102',
          addressLocality: 'New Windsor',
          addressRegion: 'NY',
          postalCode: '12553',
          addressCountry: 'US'
        }
      }
    }
  ]
};
---

<BaseLayout seo={seo}>
  <!-- ===== HERO (dark) ===== -->
  <section class="bg-neutral-950 text-white">
    <div class="container pt-28 pb-10 max-w-3xl">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-white/60">
        <span>Services</span><span class="opacity-40">•</span><span>Wellness & IV</span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="mt-2 text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Vitamin Injections</h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-white/80">
        Quick, targeted nutrient shots—such as B12, B complex, vitamin C, and custom blends—designed to support energy,
        wellness, and skin health. These therapies complement a balanced diet and medical care when needed.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-6 grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-4 gap-3 text-sm">
        <div class="rounded-xl bg-white/5 ring-1 ring-white/10 p-3">
          <div class="text-white/70">Delivery</div>
          <div class="mt-0.5 font-medium">IM / subcutaneous</div>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl bg-white/5 ring-1 ring-white/10 p-3">
          <div class="text-white/70">Session time</div>
          <div class="mt-0.5 font-medium">Minutes</div>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl bg-white/5 ring-1 ring-white/10 p-3">
          <div class="text-white/70">Downtime</div>
          <div class="mt-0.5 font-medium">None</div>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl bg-white/5 ring-1 ring-white/10 p-3">
          <div class="text-white/70">Best for</div>
          <div class="mt-0.5 font-medium">Targeted support</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== CONTENT (white) ===== -->
  <section class="bg-white text-neutral-900">
    <div class="container py-12 sm:py-14">

      <!-- Overview -->
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 items-start">
        <div class="lg:col-span-7">
          <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Overview</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-neutral-700">
            Vitamin injections deliver select nutrients directly into muscle (or subcutaneously) to bypass digestion
            and raise blood levels more rapidly than typical oral supplements. Common options include B12, B complex,
            vitamin C, and custom “boost” blends. These are supportive therapies—not a replacement for a healthy diet
            or medical treatment when a true deficiency or condition exists.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:col-span-5">
          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-neutral-50 ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-medium">Potential benefits</h3>
            <ul class="mt-3 grid grid-cols-1 gap-2 text-sm text-neutral-700">
              {[
                'Higher bioavailability than oral forms in some cases',
                'Energy support and fatigue reduction when deficiency is present (e.g., B12)',
                'Immune and antioxidant support (e.g., vitamin C)',
                'Skin-supportive blends for glow and complexion',
                'Personalized formulations under clinical oversight'
              ].map(item => (
                <li class="inline-flex items-start gap-2">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
                  <span>{item}</span>
                </li>
              ))}
            </ul>
            <p class="mt-3 text-xs text-neutral-500">
              Note: In individuals with normal vitamin levels, benefits may be modest or not clinically significant.
              Your provider will help determine appropriate options.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- What to expect -->
      <div class="mt-12 grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 items-start">
        <div class="lg:col-span-5">
          <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight">What to expect</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-neutral-700">
            We begin with a brief intake to review health history, medications, and goals. When indicated, lab work
            (such as B12 levels) may be recommended to confirm deficiency before starting a series.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:col-span-7">
          <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
              <div class="text-sm font-medium text-neutral-900">During your visit</div>
              <ul class="mt-2 text-sm text-neutral-700 space-y-1.5">
                <li>Clean, aseptic technique at the injection site</li>
                <li>IM or subcutaneous injection; mild pressure or brief sting</li>
                <li>Appointment time is typically just a few minutes</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
              <div class="text-sm font-medium text-neutral-900">Immediate feel</div>
              <ul class="mt-2 text-sm text-neutral-700 space-y-1.5">
                <li>Most return to normal activity right away</li>
                <li>Some notice a same-day or next-day lift—especially with deficiency</li>
                <li>Effects vary if baseline levels are already normal</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Popular options -->
      <div class="mt-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Popular options</h2>
        <div class="mt-4 grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
          {[
            {
              name: 'B12',
              items: ['Energy support when deficient', 'Nervous system and red blood cell support', 'Often part of weekly or monthly plans']
            },
            {
              name: 'B complex',
              items: ['Blend of key B vitamins', 'Supports metabolism and cellular energy', 'Pairs well with lifestyle changes']
            },
            {
              name: 'Vitamin C',
              items: ['Antioxidant and immune support', 'Skin-brightening synergy in some plans', 'Typically used in cycles']
            }
          ].map(card => (
            <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
              <div class="font-medium text-neutral-900">{card.name}</div>
              <ul class="mt-2 text-sm text-neutral-700 space-y-1.5">
                {card.items.map(i => <li>{i}</li>)}
              </ul>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
        <p class="mt-3 text-xs text-neutral-500">
          Custom “boost” blends can be created based on goals and medical suitability.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Aftercare -->
      <div class="mt-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Aftercare</h2>
        <div class="mt-4 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
            <ul class="text-sm text-neutral-700 space-y-2">
              <li>Keep the site clean; avoid vigorous rubbing or massage.</li>
              <li>Use a cool compress for local redness or tenderness if needed.</li>
              <li>Stay hydrated and maintain balanced nutrition.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
            <ul class="text-sm text-neutral-700 space-y-2">
              <li>Report warmth, significant redness, drainage, or persistent pain.</li>
              <li>Avoid strenuous upper-body exercise for a few hours if sore.</li>
              <li>Follow repeat-visit timing as advised by your provider.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Safety -->
      <div class="mt-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Safety & precautions</h2>
        <div class="mt-4 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-sm text-neutral-700">
          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
            <div class="font-medium text-neutral-900">Common, mild effects</div>
            <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1.5">
              <li>Temporary site soreness, redness, or small bruise</li>
              <li>Occasional itching or warmth at the site</li>
              <li>GI upset or loose stools (rare with certain vitamins)</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
            <div class="font-medium text-neutral-900">Less common, more serious</div>
            <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1.5">
              <li>Allergic reaction—seek urgent care for swelling or breathing issues</li>
              <li>Infection at the injection site (very uncommon with sterile technique)</li>
              <li>Vitamin-specific risks at high doses or with kidney/liver disease</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-4 rounded-2xl bg-neutral-50 ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5 text-sm text-neutral-700">
          <div class="font-medium text-neutral-900">Important precautions</div>
          <ul class="mt-2 list-disc list-inside space-y-1.5">
            <li>Not advised with known hypersensitivity to components.</li>
            <li>Discuss kidney/liver conditions, pregnancy, or lactation with your provider.</li>
            <li>Review all medications and supplements for potential interactions.</li>
            <li>Clinical assessment is recommended to confirm deficiency and proper dosing.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ -->
      <div class="mt-12">
        <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight">FAQ</h2>
        <div class="mt-6 grid gap-4">
          <details class="group rounded-xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
            <summary class="list-none cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-between">
              <span class="font-medium text-neutral-900">How often should I get shots?</span>
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path d="M5.8 7.3a1 1 0 011.4 0L10 10.1l2.8-2.8a1 1 0 111.4 1.4l-3.5 3.5a1 1 0 01-1.4 0L5.8 8.7a1 1 0 010-1.4z"/></svg>
            </summary>
            <p class="mt-3 text-neutral-700 text-sm">
              Frequency varies by formula, baseline levels, and goals. Plans may be weekly, biweekly, or monthly—set by your provider.
            </p>
          </details>

          <details class="group rounded-xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
            <summary class="list-none cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-between">
              <span class="font-medium text-neutral-900">Will I feel an instant energy boost?</span>
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path d="M5.8 7.3a1 1 0 011.4 0L10 10.1l2.8-2.8a1 1 0 111.4 1.4l-3.5 3.5a1 1 0 01-1.4 0L5.8 8.7a1 1 0 010-1.4z"/></svg>
            </summary>
            <p class="mt-3 text-neutral-700 text-sm">
              If you’re deficient, you may notice improvement within hours to a day. If levels are normal, effects may be subtle or not noticeable.
            </p>
          </details>

          <details class="group rounded-xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
            <summary class="list-none cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-between">
              <span class="font-medium text-neutral-900">Are shots better than oral supplements?</span>
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path d="M5.8 7.3a1 1 0 011.4 0L10 10.1l2.8-2.8a1 1 0 111.4 1.4l-3.5 3.5a1 1 0 01-1.4 0L5.8 8.7a1 1 0 010-1.4z"/></svg>
            </summary>
            <p class="mt-3 text-neutral-700 text-sm">
              In malabsorption or documented deficiency, injections can be preferable. Otherwise, differences versus oral forms may be limited.
            </p>
          </details>

          <details class="group rounded-xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
            <summary class="list-none cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-between">
              <span class="font-medium text-neutral-900">Do vitamin shots help with weight loss?</span>
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path d="M5.8 7.3a1 1 0 011.4 0L10 10.1l2.8-2.8a1 1 0 111.4 1.4l-3.5 3.5a1 1 0 01-1.4 0L5.8 8.7a1 1 0 010-1.4z"/></svg>
            </summary>
            <p class="mt-3 text-neutral-700 text-sm">
              They are not a stand-alone weight loss therapy. Addressing deficiency can support energy, but results depend on overall lifestyle and medical factors.
            </p>
          </details>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- CTA -->
      <div class="mt-12">
        <div class="rounded-2xl bg-neutral-50 ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-6 flex items-center justify-between gap-4">
          <div class="text-sm text-neutral-700">
            Interested in a personalized vitamin shot plan?
          </div>
          <a href="/contact-us/" class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-neutral-900 text-white px-5 py-2.5 text-sm hover:bg-neutral-800 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-neutral-300">
            Contact Us
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
